'''特洛伊'''（{{lang|en|'''Troy'''}}）為[[美國|美國]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[多尼芬縣_(堪薩斯州)|多尼芬縣]]的一座城市，也是多尼芬縣的[[县城|縣治]]<ref name="GR6">{{cite web|url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|accessdate=2011-06-07|title=Find a County|publisher=National Association of Counties|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQozzgAf?url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有1,010人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web|title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=2011-03-27|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218203744/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|dead-url=no}}</ref>。特洛伊為{{le|密蘇里州聖約瑟夫都會區|St. Joseph, Missouri Metropolitan Area}}的一部分。

==歷史==
[[Image:Doniphan_County_Courthouse_Troy_Kansas.jpg|thumb]]
特洛伊始建於1855年<ref>{{cite book|title=History of the State of Kansas: Containing a Full Account of Its Growth from an Uninhabited Territory to a Wealthy and Important State|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5t09AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA479|year=1883|publisher=A. T. Andreas|page=479}}</ref>。城市名以古希臘時期的城邦[[特洛伊|特洛伊]]為名<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA177#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Biennial Report of the Board of Directors of the Kansas State Historical Society | publisher=Kansas State Printing Plant | author=Kansas State Historical Society | year=1916 | pages=177 | access-date=2016-06-03 | archive-date=2014-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706200002/http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA177#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。特洛伊境內首棟住宅建於1856年，首間商店則於1857年開始營業。特洛伊在1860年成為一座已建制的城市<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Qi9cXyTWt9EC&pg=PA821#v=onepage&q&f=true | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Volume 2 | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=821 | access-date=2016-06-03 | archive-date=2014-07-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707073349/http://books.google.com/books?id=Qi9cXyTWt9EC&pg=PA821#v=onepage&q&f=true | dead-url=no }}</ref>。特洛伊首間郵政局於1857年3月16日開設<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:DP |title=Kansas Post Offices, 1828-1961 (archived) |publisher=Kansas Historical Society |accessdate=2014-06-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009130242/http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county%3ADP |archivedate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。

英國探險家[[理查德·弗朗西斯·伯顿|理查德·弗朗西斯·伯顿]]在1860年前往至加州的旅途中說道：「經過了幾個淒慘簡陋的小屋稱作特洛伊...」（"Passing through a few wretched shanties called Troy ..."）<ref>Richard Burton, (1862) ''The Look of the West 1860'', Lincoln: Univ. Nebraska Press, reprint, n.d., p.23.</ref>。

==地理==
特洛伊坐落在北緯39度47分17秒、西經95度5分27秒（亦可表示為39.788099, -95.090840）處<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110102044750/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2011-01-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|2.56|sqkm|sqmi|2}}，其中{{convert|2.54|sqkm|sqmi|2}}為陸地，{{convert|0.03|sqkm|sqmi|2}}為水域<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-date=2012-07-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

